{"tid":770182,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急)貓貓胰臟炎 求有超聲波同內窺鏡診所","createTime":"2018-08-07T01:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T18:17:41.000Z","uid":154117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a542a00d12abe6a0bd1d7a8c7cfec6b52f5d121","tid":770182,"uid":154117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:03:19.000Z","msg":"貓貓11歲由12月5.9磅急跌到最近4.2磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓貓唔係經常性嘔但餐餐都係痾爛屎<br />\n起初以為係有蟲所以2個月前係獸醫到睇左就食杜蟲藥<br />\n醫生話3個月都無改善就再睇<br />\n我見貓貓都係暴瘦忍唔到3個月就再求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n昨晚帶左佢去睇多次醫生<br />\n睇開既獸醫診所用PLI驗到佢有胰臟炎<br />\n照埋x ray個醫生搵到佢條腸有個位透射唔到<br />\n同埋醫生話照左2張x ray前後5分鐘但佢話正常會睇到腸係會郁會唔同樣 但2張x ray睇落都一樣 懷疑條腸一係唔郁一係有舊野係果個位<br />\n醫生就建議帶貓貓去照超聲波加內窺鏡<br />\n不過佢話如果佢轉介去專科會貴到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以佢建議去搵有超聲波加內窺鏡既診所<br />\n我忍唔住問個醫生其實個病痛唔痛<br />\n個醫生話係痛症 我對貓貓唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個醫生話因為個病既痛會令到貓貓唔肯食野同唔會點郁<br />\n但係我隻貓又不停咁食同不停咁痾<br />\n佢就分析唔到點解<br />\n好啦其實都係求診所各位巴打有無介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無我都一定會帶佢睇專科 我唔會比你有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/07/090256_d18b318d79830b1393f7bdb7135fc335.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2F090256_d18b318d79830b1393f7bdb7135fc335.png&h=cf2f816c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a29af3c3eaf10847fcfa9899e65bb28ae171497","tid":770182,"uid":154117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:32:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b57778829454de2074d9a1adfb276251598aa6","tid":770182,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:34:14.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"22a58f7ab3b44bf904e4b29459b6b42d38abbe7b","tid":770182,"uid":154117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b361fffae53e0a5b6a483c10e7e262d6e320c16","tid":770182,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"留tg<br />\n<br />\n你住邊區"},{"pid":"703626c79aef80843db34ccd9d0d699c9e9a8842","tid":770182,"uid":96331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:33:38.000Z","msg":"有無試過問下NPV?<br />\n唔知有無得做<br />\n但好似相對大型啲同會無咁貴"},{"pid":"3cab1e5fd3be873bf5f6585b163edd830cb7cb3a","tid":770182,"uid":44607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c8f35fd33f4be139885d2640d8aca10aadde421f","tid":770182,"uid":154117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703626c79aef80843db34ccd9d0d699c9e9a8842","tid":770182,"uid":96331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:33:38.000Z","msg":"有無試過問下NPV?<br />\n唔知有無得做<br />\n但好似相對大型啲同會無咁貴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"唔係好想去NPV<br />\n上次去過NPV check佢話乜事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實我隻貓已經瘦緊<br />\n之後去返美孚睇就驗到胰臟炎<br />\n再加上如果要內窺鏡要全身麻醉好危險<br />\n更加唔想比NPV做"},{"pid":"d64b17e5a1941871bd70d80a6826da2b6f13a5ef","tid":770182,"uid":144885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"VSH (Veterinary Specialty Hospital) Hong Kong 專科獸醫醫院<br />\n可以試呢間, 呢間好多器材, 上次帶貓去睇過, 獸醫又幾好人<br />\n佢地一般只睇 動物診所 referral, 但你可以照打去問下<br />\n<br />\nTel  2408 2588"},{"pid":"5c9589aa1f3f89d853c7003bc3a923df2c19cfc5","tid":770182,"uid":154117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64b17e5a1941871bd70d80a6826da2b6f13a5ef","tid":770182,"uid":144885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"VSH (Veterinary Specialty Hospital) Hong Kong 專科獸醫醫院<br />\n可以試呢間, 呢間好多器材, 上次帶貓去睇過, 獸醫又幾好人<br />\n佢地一般只睇 動物診所 referral, 但你可以照打去問下<br />\n<br />\nTel  2408 2588"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/07/130901_4acb6528291ad826a3bfa578bdd1f993.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2F130901_4acb6528291ad826a3bfa578bdd1f993.png&h=a2e4d02d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你要撐住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10eb0fbc80c50ce4114729d4447345c427471431","tid":770182,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"旺角Pet central"},{"pid":"8a7928173b441368d91b8aaae973f6c278b267df","tid":770182,"uid":44607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8f35fd33f4be139885d2640d8aca10aadde421f","tid":770182,"uid":154117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703626c79aef80843db34ccd9d0d699c9e9a8842","tid":770182,"uid":96331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:33:38.000Z","msg":"有無試過問下NPV?<br />\n唔知有無得做<br />\n但好似相對大型啲同會無咁貴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"唔係好想去NPV<br />\n上次去過NPV check佢話乜事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實我隻貓已經瘦緊<br />\n之後去返美孚睇就驗到胰臟炎<br />\n再加上如果要內窺鏡要全身麻醉好危險<br />\n更加唔想比NPV做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da9e4f6aef1372757dcd6a2f3c41ddc2c7015c2","tid":770182,"uid":135313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"睇專科啦<br />\n上黎問你咪又係想慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拖延多一秒隻貓就痛多一秒<br />\n屌你胰臟炎都仲諗慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢好心唔好學人養寵物"},{"pid":"8f9679b439303212a094aa4c7139d24ddca09f81","tid":770182,"uid":154117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7da9e4f6aef1372757dcd6a2f3c41ddc2c7015c2","tid":770182,"uid":135313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"睇專科啦<br />\n上黎問你咪又係想慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拖延多一秒隻貓就痛多一秒<br />\n屌你胰臟炎都仲諗慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢好心唔好學人養寵物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"胰臟炎已經醫緊<br />\n診所都開左藥去醫<br />\n有消炎抗生素杜蟲藥益生菌維他命同止痛藥<br />\n係照xray見到個怪影要再做詳細啲既檢查<br />\n唔係想慳錢 不過診所講明專科係貴到仆街<br />\n如果真係無診所有超聲波同內窺鏡設備<br />\n我一定會帶佢去睇專科<br />\n多謝巴打關心"},{"pid":"7875b79774d8fcce282efacffd894f8ad3aeb44e","tid":770182,"uid":154117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b361fffae53e0a5b6a483c10e7e262d6e320c16","tid":770182,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"留tg<br />\n<br />\n你住邊區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"葵涌<br />\n無用開tg"},{"pid":"86dd7746c095cae5e5e3c12bf50c074972bba445","tid":770182,"uid":136537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"留名 貓貓個腎點？<br />\n11歲 如果個腎麻麻 未必適合全身麻醉架啦<br />\n<br />\n我黎緊都會帶自己貓貓去照超聲波<br />\n唔貴"}]}